{"tid":986052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民不滿與建制派閉門會面　林鄭：這情緒是否有少少妒忌？","createTime":"2019-01-18T06:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T07:36:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"999d50c53f3f6b0fb308bd8e4d6d4ff7a847c456","tid":986052,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190118/s00001/bc1078e9c9fbc06da579d55b1cefcf2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190118%2Fs00001%2Fbc1078e9c9fbc06da579d55b1cefcf2f.jpg&h=4560ea9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府2月起將長者綜援申領年齡由現行60歲調高至65歲，惹來爭議不斷，被跨黨派立法會議員批評。特首林鄭月娥連同勞工及福利局長羅致光等官員，中午召開記者會宣布「補鑊」措施，林鄭月娥會上對外界批評作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，政府近日落實的社福政策，非「突然想起」，而是經多年醞釀及有理有據，惟落實執行上「大有改善空間」，自己「責無旁貸&hellip;&hellip;因此過去數日，差不多每日都要召開跨部門會議，了解究竟執行上出現了什麼問題、有何補救方法」 。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥與部分建制派閉門會面做法，引起泛民不滿，林鄭月娥質疑：「如果有部分泛民議員有這種情緒，是否有少少妒忌？或者是心不是很舒服？」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強調，若議員想與她會面，樂意安排及盡量抽時間會見，自言從來不會特別拒絕會見跨黨派議員，「但不等於行政長官沒有約見個別政黨和議員的自由」。她續指，未來兩星期難以安排會見，因下周初需要前往瑞士出席世界經濟論壇年會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190118/s00001/1547788864167/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00001%2F1547788864167%2F&d=ihaBaa%2BVjptHhFT%2F2KfPCjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=60b6129e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190118%2Fs00001%2F1547788864167%2F&h=40825a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190118/s00001/1547788864167/</a>"},{"pid":"aa92d2d2b2971b23506d18868d7dba295a5226a4","tid":986052,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"不如問，７７７既服務對象，係咪只有奶共派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edbbacd81274f15c45bc2b0e09bacf1326f8620","tid":986052,"uid":60287,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"你自己閂埋門傾哂佢得啦，仲要立法會黎做乜"},{"pid":"4e409982bc8817ccdd4e5f9b263c5e0102b4d5a6","tid":986052,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"支那式政府, 支那式管理."},{"pid":"c89b0b1338487e4100fb58a42b4e3c2de3c50dc6","tid":986052,"uid":10757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> So what? 泛民又冇人 投票輸硬冇野阻到 點解要同你班友傾"},{"pid":"d2180a10ce5bea92030a8a4ffa66c128fa544d98","tid":986052,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"好似啲港女同完其他人出街<br />\n講翻句呷醋牙 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a666b40ec046a9503bf36d11f5d6eb950c9488d","tid":986052,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"辯論<br />\n正方：泛民不滿閉門會面，係出於妒忌<br />\n反方：泛民不滿閉門會面，係出於心虛"},{"pid":"4bcb02ea91f41e8568fbcdd119bdbe071bba7bc0","tid":986052,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a666b40ec046a9503bf36d11f5d6eb950c9488d","tid":986052,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"辯論<br />\n正方：泛民不滿閉門會面，係出於妒忌<br />\n反方：泛民不滿閉門會面，係出於心虛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"辯乜野論丫<br />\n打和 super<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc86f4b4c0d9a40c33f87f859106a21be1f107cf","tid":986052,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"擺明唔撚想理佢地。"},{"pid":"786c6dedcfd50da4814ae21f6df331cd85ccb114","tid":986052,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c89b0b1338487e4100fb58a42b4e3c2de3c50dc6","tid":986052,"uid":10757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"r